Let R be a Ring. For any R-modules M, N, and P, how do we describe \mathop {	extrm {Hom}}
olimits _{R}(M\oplus N,P) in terms of \mathop {	extrm {Hom}}
olimits _{R}(M,P) and \mathop {	extrm {Hom}}
olimits _{R}(N,P)? We can draw a commutative diagram,

